<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="mr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KumbhVerse | Settings</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #ff6a00;
            --primary-glow: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.3);
            --bg-dark: #070708;
            --sidebar-bg: #0d0d0f;
            --card-bg: rgba(18, 18, 22, 0.8);
            --text-muted: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        body { background: var(--bg-dark); color: white; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; display: flex; }
        .sidebar { width: 280px; background: var(--sidebar-bg); height: 100vh; position: fixed; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 30px 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        .nav-item { color: var(--text-muted); text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 15px; margin-bottom: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; transition: 0.3s; }
        .nav-item.active { background: rgba(255, 106, 0, 0.1); color: var(--primary); }
        .main-wrapper { margin-left: 280px; width: calc(100% - 280px); padding: 40px; }
        .premium-card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 30px; padding: 30px; backdrop-filter: blur(15px); margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-control { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px; }
        .form-control:focus { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-color: var(--primary); color: white; box-shadow: none; }
        .btn-save { background: var(--primary); border: none; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: white; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-save:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--primary-glow); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <aside class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo-section mb-5 ps-2 d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
            <div style="width: 35px; height: 35px; background: var(--primary); border-radius: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;"><i class="fa-solid fa-om text-white"></i></div>
            <h4 class="m-0 fw-800">KUMBH<span style="opacity: 0.5;">VERSE</span></h4>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <a href="/admin-dashboard" class="nav-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i> Dashboard</a>
            <a href="/admin-officers" class="nav-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-users-gear"></i> Officers</a>
            <a href="/admin-crowd-map" class="nav-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i> Crowd Map</a>
            <a href="/admin-alerts" class="nav-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> Alerts</a>
            <a href="/admin-settings" class="nav-item active"><i class="fa-solid fa-gear"></i> Settings</a>
        </nav>
    </aside>

    <div class="main-wrapper">
        <header class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-800 m-0">Account Settings</h2>
            <p class="text-white-50">Manage your admin profile and system security</p>
        </header>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="premium-card">
                    <h5 class="mb-4 fw-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-circle me-2 text-primary"></i> Admin Profile</h5>
                    <form>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="small text-white-50 mb-2">FULL NAME</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" value="Master Admin">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="small text-white-50 mb-2">EMAIL ADDRESS</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" value="admin@kumbhverse.gov.in">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-save mt-3">Update Profile</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="premium-card">
                    <h5 class="mb-4 fw-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock me-2 text-primary"></i> Change Password</h5>
                    <form>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="small text-white-50 mb-2">CURRENT PASSWORD</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="••••••••">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="small text-white-50 mb-2">NEW PASSWORD</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="••••••••">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-save mt-3">Reset Password</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="premium-card" style="border-color: rgba(255, 77, 77, 0.2);">
                    <h5 class="text-danger fw-bold mb-3">Danger Zone</h5>
                    <p class="text-white-50 small">System reset किंवा सर्व डेटा डिलीट करण्यासाठी ही सेटिंग आहे. कृपया विचार करून वापरा.</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-danger rounded-pill px-4">Maintenance Mode</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>